description: Officially started in 2011, 2girls4wheels is the heart and soul of Cherish Patterson and Jamie Gruntman, two lovely and hardworking ladies determined to follow their dreams of owning their own business. They've put it all on the line in a rough economy, but are betting on themselves and are very excited to bring their delicious meals to a city block near you!Jamie and Cherish: "We are two hometown girls serving the metro area with our take on St. Louis style cuisine.  The beauty of having a mobile food truck is that we can come to you!  Whether it is a game, concert, or festival, rain or shine, count on us to be there to serve our tasty innovations.  We want locals and visitors to feel invited when they see us and we feel our truck will contribute to the energy this great city already has to offer. 2girls4wheels is our mobile creation, and serving gateway grub while showing St. Louis love is what we stand for!"See you soon!
name: 2 Girls 4 Wheels
